Name: MagicJam
About the game: Pick up a controller and join Ricky on his adventure through the 90's Funk-O-tron game machine. There are 4 different themes to choose from, each have their own weird quirks that make a unique cartoon like experience. Below is a break down of the content that early access will inlcude.Each level inlcudes 1 enemy and 1 Boss. After a year we will have another level called the Barbarian gounds that will inlcue 1 enemy and 1 Boss. Early access: ⦁ level 1: Funky Town ⦁ level 2: Roller Derby ⦁ level 3: Radical Surfing ⦁ level 4: Silver Space After a year ⦁ level 5: Barbarian grounds
